"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president has been saying that talks between the US and Iran are happening, but Iran says they are not. The US is focusing more on Iran because Ukraine needs to make a drone deal quickly.\",            \"english_title\": \"US-Iran Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que hay conversaciones entre EE.UU. e Ir\u00e1n, pero Ir\u00e1n dice que no. EE.UU. se enfoca m\u00e1s en Ir\u00e1n porque Ucrania necesita hacer un trato de drones r\u00e1pido.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones EE.UU.-Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A film claims that money and drugs are being used to make people support the ruling party. It includes quotes from voters, mayors, and a police officer.\",            \"english_title\": \"Film on Political Influence\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una pel\u00edcula dice que se usan dinero y drogas para que la gente apoye al partido gobernante. Incluye citas de votantes, alcaldes y un polic\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pel\u00edcula sobre Influencia Pol\u00edtica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The disruption in oil supplies has led to shortages and worries in several African countries.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oil Supply Issues\",            \"translated_version\": \"La interrupci\u00f3n en el suministro de petr\u00f3leo ha causado escasez y preocupaciones en varios pa\u00edses africanos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Problemas de Suministro de Petr\u00f3leo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A judge emphasized the importance of the right to defense as prosecutors argued that a couple should not use Venezuelan funds to pay their lawyers.\",            \"english_title\": \"Right to Defense\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un juez destac\u00f3 la importancia del derecho a la defensa mientras los fiscales dec\u00edan que una pareja no deber\u00eda usar fondos venezolanos para pagar a sus abogados.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Derecho a la Defensa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Court of Human Rights ruled in favor of Noelia Castillo earlier this week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Court Ruling\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Corte Europea de Derechos Humanos decidi\u00f3 a favor de Noelia Castillo esta semana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Decisi\u00f3n de la Corte\"        }    ]}"